{"tid":2263094,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"參考x發明咗個便攜式水力發電機","createTime":"2020-10-29T15:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T22:42:39.000Z","uid":319228,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5c80cb71c3b8cef0eb3827d595d389bef0b3d936","tid":2263094,"uid":319228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:10:53.000Z","msg":"水力發電望落好似好大型，<br />\n<br />\n但係其實都可以便攜，好似尿袋咁 隨身攜帶，<br />\n<br />\n利用人類身上嘅 尿 就可以輕鬆發電<br />\n<br />\n一般成人每日排尿8次，每次裝滿約300ml，<br />\n<br />\n一年即876 000ml，絕不可輕視<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我參考咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VEGzVqB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVEGzVqB.png&h=3754ae54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrkXTci.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrkXTci.jpg&h=c87ba683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發明咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HsvH4i6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHsvH4i6.jpg&h=55e6deac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原理係將尿液集中 流動中的尿推動輪機使之旋轉<br />\n<br />\n再通過發電機發電 原理同水力發電一樣<br />\n<br />\n只不過由水變成尿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n運作圖如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K70kRHW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK70kRHW.gif&h=a8733836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電力可以儲起 遲啲用 <br />\n<br />\n或者可以即刻放電 幫啲尿充電<br />\n<br />\n用嚟攻擊/自衛一流<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z3QkRKQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3QkRKQ.gif&h=1206e247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又或者純粹當電池用都得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QGkkRNT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQGkkRNT.gif&h=167e222e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2升尿大約可以照明10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n10升可以幫iPhone 12 叉10%電<br />\n<br />\n10 000升可以幫tesla 叉10公里<br />\n<br />\n10 000（10 000次方）升可以滿足港島一日嘅用電<br />\n<br />\n「戴上一小套，文明一大步」"},{"pid":"83f8956adfe77a232a849d2982ce1532c5374299","tid":2263094,"uid":38904,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"乖<br />\n唔好學其他會員啲style<br />\n好7"},{"pid":"5aaa019a70fb93906e776802b8b6fc772d5d2d98","tid":2263094,"uid":366515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:16:07.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩姐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ee10d4beed3cb70a4ee8765dee5dc45ac43ea3","tid":2263094,"uid":319228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:18:13.000Z","msg":"大家俾啲想像力得唔得"},{"pid":"7e6b08aa5e24fa3b37ffcd4d69bffec42481dbe4","tid":2263094,"uid":373270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76ee10d4beed3cb70a4ee8765dee5dc45ac43ea3","tid":2263094,"uid":319228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:18:13.000Z","msg":"大家俾啲想像力得唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:22:33.000Z","msg":"咁不如整 行步發電機"},{"pid":"f4cefa221b37a7d964127b131954b4589a9e708f","tid":2263094,"uid":319228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e6b08aa5e24fa3b37ffcd4d69bffec42481dbe4","tid":2263094,"uid":373270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76ee10d4beed3cb70a4ee8765dee5dc45ac43ea3","tid":2263094,"uid":319228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:18:13.000Z","msg":"大家俾啲想像力得唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:22:33.000Z","msg":"咁不如整 行步發電機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:23:37.000Z","msg":"Why not both"},{"pid":"c89a7064bd8e17280d0fb9a25872c27dcf638e19","tid":2263094,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:25:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dca708d79d78fdd0ebcd7b930ee31547bfd710de","tid":2263094,"uid":37144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"咁佢去得唔夠快嗰陣咪會浸住條嘢